quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  38,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  38,1,Saaad qasam hai is quran ki jo nasiyaat dainay wala hai ( ke tum haq par ho )
  38,2,magar jo log kafir hain woh ghuroor aur mukhalfat mein hain
  38,3,hum ne un se pehlay bohat si amtoN ko halaak kardiya to woh ( azaab ke waqt ) lagey faryaad karne aur woh rihayi ka waqt nahi tha
  38,4,aur unhon ne taajjubkiya ke un ke paas un hi mein se hadaayat karne wala aaya aur kafir kehnay lagey ke yeh to jadugar hai jhoota
  38,5,kiya is ne itnay mabodon ki jagah aik hi mabood bana diya. yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai
  38,6,to un mein jo Muaziz they woh chal kharray hue ( aur bolay ) ke chalo aur apne mabodon ( ki pooja ) par qaim raho. be shak yeh aisi baat hai jis se ( tum par Sharfo fazilat ) maqsood hai
  38,7,yeh pichlle mazhab mein hum ne kabhi suni hi nahi. yeh bilkul banai hui baat hai
  38,8,kiya hum sab mein se isi par nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) utreen hai? ( nahi ) balkay yeh meri nasiyaat ki kitaab se shak mein hain. balkay unhon ne abhi mere azaab ka maza nahi chakkha
  38,9,kiya un ke paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat ke khazanay hain jo ghalib aur bohat ataa karne wala hai
  38,10,ya asmano aur zameen aur jo kuch un mein hai un ( sab ) par un hi ki hukoomat hai. to chahiye ke rasiyaan taan kar ( asmano ) par charh jayen
  38,11,yahan shikast khaye hue garohoon mein se yeh bhi aik lashkar hai
  38,12,un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur Aad aur mekho+A4082 wala firaon ( aur is ki qoum ke log ) bhi jhutla chuke hain
  38,13,aur smod aur Loot ki qoum aur ban ke rehne walay bhi. yahi woh giroh hain
  38,14,( un ) sab ne payghambaroon ko jhtlaya to mera azaab ( un par ) aa waqay howa
  38,15,"aur yeh log to sirf aik zor ki aawaz ka jis mein ( shuru hue peechay ) kuch waqfa nahi hoga, intzaar karte hain"
  38,16,aur kehte hain ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko hamara hissa hisaab ke din se pehlay hi day day
  38,17,( ae paighambar ) yeh jo kuch kehte hain is par sabr karo. aur hamaray bande dawod ko yaad karo jo sahib qowat they ( aur ) be shak woh rujoo karne walay they
  38,18,hum ne pahoron ko un ke zair farmaan kardiya tha ke subah vsham un ke sath ( khuday-e ) pak ( ka ) zikar karte they
  38,19,aur parindon ko bhi ke jama rehtay they. sab un ke farmanbardar they
  38,20,aur hum ne un ki badshahi ko mustahkamkiya aur un ko hikmat ataa ki aur ( khusumat ki ) baat ka faisla ( sikhaya )
  38,21,bhala tumahray paas un jhagrnay walon ki bhi khabar aayi hai jab woh deewar phaand kar ibadat khanaay mein daakhil hue
  38,22,jis waqt woh dawod ke paas aeye to woh un se ghabra gay unhon ne kaha ke khauf nah kijiye. hum dono ka aik muqadma hai ke hum mein se aik ne dosray par zayad-ti ki hai to aap hum mein insaaf ka faisla kar dijiye aur be insafi nah kijiye ga aur hum ko seedha rasta dikha dijiye
  38,23,( kefiyat yeh hai ke ) yeh mera bhai hai is ke ( haan ) ninanway dumbiyan hain aur mere ( paas ) aik dumbi hai. yeh kehta hai ke yeh bhi mere hawalay kardey aur guftagu mein mujh par zabardasti karta hai
  38,24,unhon ne kaha ke yeh jo teri dunbi mangta hai ke apni dumbiyon mein milale be shak tujh par zulm karta hai. aur aksar shareek aik dosray par zayad-ti hikiya karte hain. haan jo imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay aur aisay log bohat kam hain. aur dawod ne khayaalkiya ke ( is waqeye se ) hum ne un ko aazmaaya hai to unhon ne apne perwar-digaar se mughfirat mangi aur jhuk kar gur parre aur ( khuda ki taraf ) rujookiya
  38,25,to hum ne un ko bakhash diya. aur be shak un ke liye hamaray haan qurb aur umdah maqam hai
  38,26,ae dawod hum ne tum ko zameen mein badshah banaya hai to logon mein insaaf ke faislaykiya karo aur khwahish ki pairwi nah karna ke woh tumhe khuda ke raste se bhatka day gi. jo log khuda ke raste se bhataktay hain un ke liye sakht azaab ( tayyar ) hai ke unhon ne hisaab ke din ko bhala diya
  38,27,aur hum ne aasman aur zameen ko aur jo kaayenaat un mein hai is ko khaali az Maslehat nahi pedakiya. yeh un ka gumaan hai jo kafir hain. so kafiroon ke liye dozakh ka azaab hai
  38,28,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay.kiya un ko hum un ki terhan kar den ge jo malik mein fasaad karte hain. ya parhaiz garon ko badkaaron ki terhan kar den ge
  38,29,( yeh ) kitaab jo hum ne tum par nazil ki hai babarkat hai taakay log is ki aayton mein ghhor karen aur taakay ahal aqal nasiyaat pakren
  38,30,aur hum ne dawod ko Sulaiman ataa kiye. bohat khoob bande ( they aur ) woh ( khuda ki taraf ) rujoo karne walay they
  38,31,jab un ke samnay shaam ko khasay ke ghoray paish kiye gay
  38,32,to kehnay lagey ke mein ne apne perwar-digaar ki yaad se ( ghaafil ho kar ) maal ki mohabbat ikhtiyar ki. yahan taq ke ( aftaab ) parday mein choup gaya
  38,33,( bolay ke ) un ko mere paas wapas le aao. phir un ki tangon aur gardnon par haath phairnay lagey
  38,34,aur hum ne Sulaiman ki azmaish ki aur un ke takhat par aik dhar daal diya phir unhon ne ( khuda ki taraf ) rujookiya
  38,35,( aur ) dua ki ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe mughfirat kar aur mujh ko aisi badshahi ataa kar ke mere baad kisi ko Shayaan nah ho. be shak to bara ataa frmane wala hai
  38,36,phir hum ne howa ko un ke zeray farman kardiya ke jahan woh pohanchna chahtay un ke hukum se naram naram chalne lagti
  38,37,aur دیووں ko bhi ( un ke zeray farman kiya ) woh sab emiratein bananay walay aur ghouta maarny walay they
  38,38,aur ouron ko bhi jo zanjeeroon mein jakray hue they
  38,39,( hum ne kaha ) yeh hamari bakhshish hai ( chaho ) to ahsaan karo ya ( chaho to ) rakh chhorro ( tum se ) kuch hisaab nahi hai
  38,40,aur be shak un ke liye hamaray haan qurb aur umdah maqam hai
  38,41,aur hamaray bande ayub ko yaad karo jab unhon ne apne rab ko puraka ke ( baar ilhaa ) shetan ne mujh ko aeza aur takleef day rakhi hai
  38,42,( hum ne kaha ke zameen par ) laat maro ( dekho ) yeh ( chashma nikal aaya ) nahanay ko thanda aur peenay ko ( sheree )
  38,43,aur hum ne un ko ahal o Ayal aur un ke sath un ke barabar aur bakhshay. ( yeh ) hamari taraf se rehmat aur aqal walon ke liye nasiyaat thi
  38,44,aur apne haath mein jharoo lau aur is se maro aur qasam nah torro. be shak hum ne un ko saabit qadam paaya. bohat khoob bande they be shak woh rujoo karne walay they
  38,45,aur hamaray bundon ibrahim aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob ko yaad karo jo hathon walay aur aankhon walay they
  38,46,hum ne un ko aik ( sift ) khaas ( akhirat ke ) ghar ki yaad se mumtazkiya tha
  38,47,aur hamaray nazdeek munhtakhib aur naik logon mein se they
  38,48,aur asmayl aur Tasa'a aur zalkifil ko yaad karo. woh sab naik logon mein se they
  38,49,yeh nasiyaat hai aur parhaiz garon ke liye to umdah maqam hai
  38,50,hamesha rehne ke baagh jin ke darwazay un ke liye khulay hon ge
  38,51,un mein takyay lagaye baithy hon ge aur ( khanay peenay ke liye ) bohat se meway aur sharaab mngwate rahen ge
  38,52,aur un ke paas neechi nigah rakhnay wali ( aur ) hum Umar ( aurtain ) hon gi
  38,53,yeh woh cheeze hain jin ka hisaab ke din ke liye tum se wadakiya jata tha
  38,54,yeh hamara rizaq hai jo kabhi khatam nahi hoga
  38,55,yeh ( naematain to farmabardaron ke liye hain ) aur sarkashon ke liye bura thikana hai
  38,56,( yani ) dozakh. jis mein woh daakhil hon ge aur woh buri aaraam gaah hai
  38,57,yeh kholta howa garam pani aur peep ( hai ) ab is ke mazay chakhain
  38,58,aur isi terhan ke aur bohat se ( azaab hon ge )
  38,59,yeh aik fouj hai jo tumahray sath daakhil hogi. un ko khusi nah ho yeh dozakh mein jaane walay hain
  38,60,kahin ge balkay tum hi ko khusi nah ho. tum hi to yeh ( bulaa ) hamaray samnay laaye so ( yeh ) bura thikana hai
  38,61,woh kahin ge ae perwar-digaar jo is ko hamaray samnay laya hai is ko dozakh mein dona azaab day
  38,62,aur kahin gekiya sabab hai ke ( yahan ) hum un shakhson ko nahi dekhte jin ko baaroon mein shumaar karte they
  38,63,kiya hum ne un se thattha اkiya hai ya ( hamari ) ankhen un ( ki taraf ) se phir gayi hain ?
  38,64,be shak yeh ahal dozakh ka jhagarna brhq hai
  38,65,keh do ke mein to sirf hadaayat karne wala hon. aur khuday-e yaktaa aur ghalib ke siwa koi mabood nahi
  38,66,jo asmano aur zameen aur jo makhlooq un mein hai sab ka maalik hai ghalib ( aur ) bakhsnay wala
  38,67,keh do ke yeh aik barri ( holnaak cheez ki ) khabar hai
  38,68,jis ko tum dheyaan mein nahi laatay
  38,69,mujh ko oopar ki majlis ( walon ) ka jab woh jhagarte they kuch bhi ilm nah tha
  38,70,meri taraf to yahi wahi ki jati hai ke mein khullam khula hadaayat karne wala hon
  38,71,jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne firshton se kaha ke mein matti se ensaan bananay wala hon
  38,72,jab is ko durust karloon aur is mein apni rooh phoonk dun to is ke agay sjday mein gir parna
  38,73,to tamam firshton ne sajdakiya
  38,74,magar shetan akarr betha aur kafiroon mein hogaya
  38,75,khuda ne ) farmaya ke ae iblees jis shakhs ko mein ne apne hathon se banaya is ke agay sajda karne se tujhe kis cheez ne manakiya.kiya to ghuroor mein agaya ya ounchay darjay walon mein tha ?
  38,76,bola ke mein is se behtar hon ( ke ) to ne mujh ko ko aag se pedakiya aur isay matti se banaya
  38,77,farmaya yahan se nikal ja to mardood hai
  38,78,aur tujh par qayamat ke din taq meri laanat ( padtee ) rahay gi
  38,79,kehnay laga ke mere perwar-digaar mujhe is roz taq ke log uthaye jayen mohlat day
  38,80,farmaya ke tujh ko mohlat di jati hai
  38,81,is roz taq jis ka waqt muqarrar hai
  38,82,kehnay laga ke mujhe teri izzat ki qasam mein un sab ko بہکاتا rahon ga
  38,83,siwa un ke jo tairay khalis bande hain
  38,84,farmaya sach ( hai ) aur mein bhi sach kehta hon
  38,85,ke mein tujh se aur jo un mein se teri pairwi karen ge sab se jahannum ko bhar dun ga
  38,86,ae paighambar keh do ke mein tum se is ka sila nahi mangta aur nah mein banawat karne walon mein hon
  38,87,yeh quran to ahal aalam ke liye nasiyaat hai
  38,88,aur tum ko is ka haal aik waqt ke baad maloom hojaye ga
